<text><body>
<lb n="0739a05" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0739a06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0739a07" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0739001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此經明本也以宋本元本宮本知本對校，〔佛說…經〕六字－【知】</note><app n="0739001" word-count="6"><lem wit="【大】"><title>佛說時非時經</title></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0739001" place="foot" type="rest">此經明本也以宋本元本宮本知本對校</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0739a08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0739a09" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0739002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝外國【宮】，〔天竺…譯〕十字－【知】</note><note n="0739002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔天竺三藏法師若羅嚴譯〕十字－【知】，天竺三藏＝外國【宮】</note><app n="0739002"><lem wit="【大】">天竺三藏法師若羅嚴譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">外國法師若羅嚴譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0739a10" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT17p0739a1001">如是我聞：</p><p id="pT17p0739a1005" place="inline">一時，佛住王舍城迦蘭陀竹<note n="0739003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔林〕－【知】</note><app n="0739003"><lem wit="【大】">林</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0739a11" ed="T"/>園精舍。</p><p id="pT17p0739a1104" place="inline"><note n="0739004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（是）＋時【知】</note><app n="0739004"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">是時</rdg></app>，佛告諸比丘：「我當為汝說時
<lb n="0739a12" ed="T"/><note n="0739005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（與）＋非【知】</note><app n="0739005"><lem wit="【大】">非</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">與非</rdg></app>時經，善思<note n="0739006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念之＝憶念【知】</note><app n="0739006"><lem wit="【大】">念之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">憶念</rdg></app>！」</p><p id="pT17p0739a1208" place="inline">諸比丘言：「<note n="0739007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如是〕－【宮】</note><app n="0739007"><lem wit="【大】">如是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>，世
<lb n="0739a13" ed="T"/>尊！<note n="0739008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝謹【知】</note><app n="0739008"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">謹</rdg></app>受教聽。」</p><p id="pT17p0739a1306" place="inline">佛告諸比丘：「是中何者為
<lb n="0739a14" ed="T"/>時？何者為非時？比丘當知。</p>
<lb n="0739a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a1501">「冬初<note n="0739009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔分〕－【知】＊</note><app n="0739009"><lem wit="【大】">分</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>，</p>
<lb n="0739a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a1601">「<note n="0739010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔第一〕－【知】＊</note><app n="0739010"><lem wit="【大】">第一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>十五日，七&CB00560;為時，四&CB00560;半<note n="0739011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（為）＋非時【知】下同</note><app n="0739011"><lem wit="【大】">非時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">為非時</rdg></app>；</p>
<lb n="0739a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a1701">「<note n="0739012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔從…日〕十字－【知】，以下知恩院本非時下總無從乃至　等期日</note><app n="0739012" word-count="10"><lem wit="【大】">從八月十六日至三十日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0739012" place="foot" type="rest">以下知恩院本非時下總無從乃至　等期日</note>。</p>
<lb n="0739a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a1801">「第二十五日，八&CB00560;為時，六&CB00560;八指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a1901">「從九月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a2001">「第三十五日，九&CB00560;為時，七&CB00560;六指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a2101">「從九月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a2201">「第四十五日，十&CB00560;為時，八&CB00560;三指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a2301">「從十月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739a24" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a2401">「第五十五日，十一&CB00560;為時，九&CB00560;<note n="0739013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四指〕－【知】</note><app n="0739013"><lem wit="【大】">四指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>非時；</p>
<lb n="0739a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a2501">「從十月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a2601">「第六十五日，十二&CB00560;為時，十一&CB00560;六指非
<lb n="0739a27" ed="T"/>時；</p><p id="pT17p0739a2702" place="inline">「從十一月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739a2801">「第七十五日，十一&CB00560;半為時，十&CB00560;三指非
<lb n="0739a29" ed="T"/>時；</p><p id="pT17p0739a2902" place="inline">「從十一月十六日至三十日。</p>
<pb n="0739b" ed="T" id="T17.0794b.0739b"/>
<lb n="0739b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b0101">「第八十五日，十一&CB00560;為時，九&CB00560;四指非<note n="0739014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＋（冬四月竟）夾註【知】</note><app n="0739014"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">時<note place="inline">冬四月竟</note></rdg></app>；</p>
<lb n="0739b02" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b0201">「從十二月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b0301">「春初<app type="＊" source="0739009"><lem wit="【大】">分</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>，</p>
<lb n="0739b04" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b0401">「<app type="＊" source="0739010"><lem wit="【大】">第一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>十五日，十&CB00560;為時，八&CB00560;<note n="0739015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔少〕－【知】</note><app n="0739015"><lem wit="【大】">少</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>三指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b0501">「從十二月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b0601">「第二十五日，九&CB00560;半為時，七&CB00560;少三指非
<lb n="0739b07" ed="T"/>時；</p><p id="pT17p0739b0702" place="inline">「從正月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b0801">「第三十五日，九&CB00560;為時，六&CB00560;少三指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b0901">「從正月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1001">「第四十五日，八&CB00560;為時，五&CB00560;<note n="0739016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔少三指〕－【知】</note><app n="0739016"><lem wit="【大】">少三指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>非時；</p>
<lb n="0739b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1101">「從二月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1201">「第五十五日，七&CB00560;為時，<note n="0739017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝四【知】</note><app n="0739017"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">四</rdg></app>&CB00560;少三指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1301">「從二月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1401">「第六十五日，六&CB00560;為時，三&CB00560;少四指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1501">「從三月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1601">「第七十五日，五&CB00560;為時，三&CB00560;少三指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1701">「從三月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1801">「第八十五日，四&CB00560;為時，二&CB00560;少一指非<note n="0739018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＋（春四月竟）夾註【知】</note><app n="0739018"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">時<note place="inline">春四月竟</note></rdg></app>；</p>
<lb n="0739b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b1901">「從四月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b2001">「夏初<app type="＊" source="0739009"><lem wit="【大】">分</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>，</p>
<lb n="0739b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b2101">「<app type="＊" source="0739010"><lem wit="【大】">第一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>十五日，三&CB00560;為時，二&CB00560;少四指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b2201">「從四月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b2301">「第二十五日，二&CB00560;為時，一&CB00560;少五指非時；</p>
<lb n="0739b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b2401">「從五月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b2501">「第三十五日，二&CB00560;半為時，一&CB00560;<note n="0739019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">少三指＝半【知】</note><app n="0739019"><lem wit="【大】">少三指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">半</rdg></app>非
<lb n="0739b26" ed="T"/>時；</p><p id="pT17p0739b2602" place="inline">「從五月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b2701">「第四十五日，三&CB00560;半為時，二&CB00560;少二指非
<lb n="0739b28" ed="T"/>時；</p><p id="pT17p0739b2802" place="inline">「從六月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739b2901">「第五十五日，四&CB00560;半為時，二&CB00560;半非時；</p>
<pb n="0739c" ed="T" id="T17.0794b.0739c"/>
<lb n="0739c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739c0101">「從六月十六日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739c0201">「第六十五日，五&CB00560;為時，三&CB00560;非時；</p><p id="pT17p0739c0214" place="inline">「從七
<lb n="0739c03" ed="T"/>月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739c0401">「第七十五日，五&CB00560;半為時，三&CB00560;半非時。</p>
<lb n="0739c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739c0501">「從七月十<note n="0739020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">六＝五【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0739020"><lem wit="【大】">六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">五</rdg></app>日至三十日。</p>
<lb n="0739c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739c0601">「第八十五日，六&CB00560;為時，四&CB00560;<note n="0739021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔半〕－【知】</note><app n="0739021"><lem wit="【大】">半</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>非<note n="0739022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＋（夏四月竟）夾註【知】</note><app n="0739022"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">時<note place="inline">夏四月竟</note></rdg></app>；</p>
<lb n="0739c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739c0701">「從八月一日至十五日。</p>
<lb n="0739c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739c0801">「如是，諸比丘！我已說十二月時非時，為諸
<lb n="0739c09" ed="T"/>聲聞<note n="0739023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【知】</note><app n="0739023"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app>所應<note n="0739024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝作【知】</note><app n="0739024"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">作</rdg></app>，憐愍利益故說。我所應
<lb n="0739c10" ed="T"/><note n="0739025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【知】</note><app n="0739025"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT17p0739c01"/>已竟，汝等當行。若樹<note n="0739026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝下【宮】</note><app n="0739026"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">下</rdg></app>空處，露坐
<lb n="0739c11" ed="T"/>思惟。諸比丘！莫為放逸，後致悔恨，是我所
<lb n="0739c12" ed="T"/>教戒。」佛說<note n="0739027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經竟＝是法【知】</note><app n="0739027"><lem wit="【大】">經竟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">是法</rdg></app>。</p><p id="pT17p0739c1207" place="inline">時諸比丘，皆大歡喜，<note n="0739028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔勸助〕－【知】</note><app n="0739028"><lem wit="【大】">勸
<lb n="0739c13" ed="T"/>助</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0739029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受持＝奉行【知】</note><app n="0739029"><lem wit="【大】">受持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">奉行</rdg></app>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0739c14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><title>佛說時非時經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0739c15" ed="T"/><div1 type="W"><lg id="lgT17p0739c1501" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「因緣輕慢故，</l><l>命終墮<note n="0739030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">地獄＝惡道【知】</note><app n="0739030"><lem wit="【大】">地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">惡道</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0739c16" ed="T"/><l>因緣修善者，</l><l>於此生天上，</l>
<lb n="0739c17" ed="T"/><l>緣斯修善業，</l><l>離惡得解脫，</l>
<lb n="0739c18" ed="T"/><l>不善<note n="0739031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝觀【知】</note><app n="0739031"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">觀</rdg></app>因緣，</l><l>身壞入惡道。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0739c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0739c1901"><note n="0739032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝外國【宮】，〔天竺…訖〕二十七字－【知】</note><note n="0739032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔天竺三藏法師若羅嚴手執梵本口自宣譯涼州道人于闐城中寫訖〕二十七字－【知】，天竺三藏＝外國【宮】</note><app n="0739032"><lem wit="【大】">天竺三藏法師若羅嚴，手執<note n="0739033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梵＝胡【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0739033"><lem wit="【大】">梵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">胡</rdg></app>本，口自
<lb n="0739c20" ed="T"/>宣譯。涼州道人，<note n="0739034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于闐＝釬&CB07018;【宮】</note><app n="0739034"><lem wit="【大】">于闐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">釬&CB07018;</rdg></app>城中寫訖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【知】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">外國法師若羅嚴手執梵本口自宣譯涼州道人于闐城中寫訖</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0739c21" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT17p0739c2101" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「披褐懷玉，</l><l>深智作愚，</l><l>外如夷人，</l>
<lb n="0739c22" ed="T"/><l>內懷明珠，</l><l>千億萬劫，</l><l>與道同軀。」<note n="0739035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下知恩院本有經題並光明皇后願文</note></l></lg></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>